{"tid":306823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個仔比共產黨逼害","createTime":"2017-07-03T00:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T17:33:19.000Z","uid":124682,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cb606650787cb4aca904e28c9e475dd0bd102fb2","tid":306823,"uid":124682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:32:52.000Z","msg":"自從佢比幾個東北壯漢雞姦左之後<br />\n精神就有少少問題<br />\n個次因爲用廣東話屌人老母<br />\n點知人地係好大粒既官<br />\n就咁比人捉左去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後黎佢一唔食藥就會係咁講書面語<br />\n煩到大家真係唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaa97b26d8d160b762bfefef53b8d7e5c3cefaf","tid":306823,"uid":111571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d96e2eff077dfdd9561e0c8a69160e47943eb0b","tid":306823,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:51:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bd75bf1cbdc2ebf8df87fc4ab54f9deeaf630b0","tid":306823,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T00:52:59.000Z","msg":"原來背後有咁辛酸嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0769b066fccb89f1798f4d7cda65f1fb511d0d","tid":306823,"uid":124682,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T01:22:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不要誹謗我</blockquote><br />\n啊仔 你唔好再逃避啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b688d95299a1fcc1874fe900bf0b79711681bf","tid":306823,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"快啲捉佢去人道毀滅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e2fa5025aa01b63800124263ba346dd6bbb4027","tid":306823,"uid":124682,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伯母辛苦你啦，呢排咁多人屌你有冇生花柳?</blockquote><br />\n講得出既都生曬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都要死頂啦<br />\n鬼叫個仔唔爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca7a31442dedb7dd9729faa1e08c03690f1ac9a","tid":306823,"uid":145230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T17:33:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}